Ladies, seriously, do take note of how you sit especially when you are wearing a dress/skirt that ends above your knees. Having a big bag to put on your lap doesn't mean that noone can see underneath your skirt. I have no wish to see your hot pink lacy thong or baby blue bikni panty peering at me throughout the train ride. And when you uncross your legs to shift into&nbsp;a more comfortable position, try not to flash your underwear. It's disgusting and disturbing.&nbsp;

Oh yes, even if you think your thighs are thick enough to cover, don't.&nbsp;It's a sight for sore eyes.

My laptop died on me - hard disk burnt.
All my data is lost; my schoolwork, jcrc files, music &amp; movies and whatnots. Kapish! Nothing can be retrieved.&nbsp;

LJing on baby's comp right now.

Today is a fucking bad day. No studying will be done today.&nbsp;

When shit happens, it all happens at the same time. How fucked up is that

Just as how everything becomes one big fat lie, and all I'm to do is just sit back and pretend nothing ever happened.

This is the life I don't want to live in. Yet such is the life I've to endure.&nbsp;

And while I sit here, with my laptop screen as the sole light source, I can feel the piercings of your work - slow but penetrating.
